short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Agapa Session Manager helps you to save your opened tabs and windows and restore them whenever you want.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With Agapa Session Manager you can save you current browser windows and tabs and restore them whenever you want.
Supports multiple sessions, save session to file, import session from file.
